field.description: Port D reset bit y (y = 0..15) These bits are write-only and can be accessed in word, half-word or byte mode. A read to these bits returns the value 0x0000. 0: No action on the corresponding ODRx bit 1: Resets the corresponding ODRx bit Note: If both BSx and BRx are set, BSx has priority.
